pub unsafe extern "C" fn enable_formatted_log_line_tracing(
    callback: TracingLogLineFn,
    max_level: Level,
    format: LogLineFormat,
    ansi: bool,
    with_time: bool,
    with_level: bool,
    with_target: bool,
) -> bool {
    setup_log_line_subscriber(
        callback,
        max_level,
        format,
        ansi,
        with_time,
        with_level,
        with_target,
    )
    .is_ok()
}
